requirement.description:
The HAL/pwm16bit module shall provide the following functionality:
\begin{itemize}
    \item Configuration of outputs for PWM generation with selectable pre-scaler and maximum value.
    \item Configuration of duty-cycle per channel
\end{itemize}
for each of the tree outputs for each of the three timers.

The HAL/timer8bit module shall provide the following functionality:
\begin{itemize}
    \item Configuration of the timer prescaler
    \item Signalling of timer overflows via callback
\end{itemize}
